text: Nizhnegaleyevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Verkhnegaleyevsky Selsoviet, Zilairsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 2 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 80 km from Zilair, 2 km from Verkhnegaleyevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zilairsky District
title: Nizhnegaleyevo
